@startuml
title Where cain sits in the four-corner card model
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #F1ECF9
  BorderColor #6E4FA8
}
skinparam ArrowColor #6E4FA8
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #F1ECF9
skinparam noteBorderColor #6E4FA8

actor Cardholder as CH
[Acceptor\n(merchant / ATM)] as ACC
[Acquirer] as ACQ
[Issuer] as ISS

CH --> ACC : presents card
ACC --> ACQ : caaa (POS) / catp (ATM)
ACQ --> ISS : cain messages
ISS --> CH : holds the account
note bottom of ACQ : cain carries the acquirer-to-issuer legs\n(often via a card scheme network)
@enduml
